{"items": [{"shortCode": "DZcTvtmS4-7", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DZcTvtmS4-7/", "caption": "Which one are you trying first? \ud83d\udccc save this for later! \n1. Remove pet hair and fluff from your clothes by adding a baby wipe to your load. It need to be a very thick, good quality wipe that won\u2019t disintegrate in the wash, and you may need 2-3 depending on how much hair is on the clothes. The baby wipe creates static that attracts the hair and fluff so it stays away from your clothes. \n2. Remove oil stains by covering with baking soda and ironing with baking paper\n3. You guys know how much I love to place linen spray on cotton balls inside your vacuum to make your home smell amazing. Just remember to empty your vacuum canister once you\u2019re finished cleaning xx \n\nHope these were helpful lovelies \u2665\ufe0f\u2665\ufe0f\n\n#homehacks #hometips #homesweethome #homefragrance #tipsandtricks", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T10:32:31.000Z", "videoDuration": 21.801, "videoPlayCount": 154795, "videoViewCount": 65869, "likesCount": 1760, "commentsCount": 9, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/722809455_18097315484190993_358499713789046703_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHXH804GDp5bKptkwsxbzTMmKgyu1XimJ_M8wPRwENsUkL4GrZ2MPD2cUXC9Qckdow&_nc_ohc=3cztjX9rosEQ7kNvwG8w9Rp&_nc_gid=kJKhbWh-bLt-D7gE67qtsA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af8wrw_qB1zikM68hVMjAkcrmmQ3Z4zVslDpKgyA-VtYJw&oe=6A3123B0&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQO8Ac22oSaP9Tqtirl3beAyUgMPXDFcmSoivpgAeys2Gu5eFEpc9bHK2tcE9icDTExZgWSql8PyPZBtFRYXETwEGb8coW5gNAWm6Qw.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=108&vs=2244956512577160_1896479638&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=6f969e70dd&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af_BXMMpKnkrabtm770wzSecuQGaw4VPkOR