ry first?\n1. Fit more clothes in your suitcase by packing it vertically\n2. Place essential oil on cotton balls to keep clothes smelling fresh\n3. Pack belts around your suitcase to save space\n4. Use your suitcase lining to seperate slippers\n5. Squeeze air out of toiletries to prevent them leaking\n6. And you can also use silicone lids to prevent spills. These ones are from Amazon \n7. Prevent necklaces tangling by placing them through a straw\n8. And use a button to keep earrings together\n9. Stuff shoes with socks or chargers to save space\n10. And always place an @apple AirTag in your suitcase so you can track it in case it goes missing\n\nHope these quick tricks were helpful lovelies xx \n\n#suitcasepacking #packwithme #viraltips #tipsandtricks", "timestamp": "2026-05-17T08:51:50.000Z", "videoDuration": 32.6, "videoPlayCount": 602925, "videoViewCount": 302844, "likesCount": 8193, "commentsCount": 43, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/701726081_18094642703190993_8554778577437556244_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFmZQC_NiEClCA9qrXhcc_jCalQmlaf5n5qeXu23E7zRvnrJW3Z8N00BmoOYmtyxdmpsoRecUOmvXqg0RtVKbJa&_nc_ohc=aNDAXjLpRd0Q7kNvwHj3otc&_nc_gid=0Oex2-8Rx77aVVL9J8uHHg&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_KMa0bWSaDNKsL9U8vpGBF7mIF4THaQku8VAfF_YGLEg&oe=6A313E5A&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQMl-ftX8JKWPnotYcSsVnGqMTEU4ndtFtOMUHh5xxn3zeTNAIiqrm2BcbVY3GXiTTSgfA5HpHQ5P4NNKuzugk1kf7kCkXcvruYSEfM.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=106&vs=900838586309257_1975652559&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=5c0ac95ca3&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af-G_PFSgiskEGNNeFv3CYp7GgLiUuhOTfgWWASWRlVEbg&oe=6A2D1B29&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "mama_mila_au", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": tr